---
ai_image: true
title: Cinnamon Sugar Toast
tags: breakfast, snacks, kid-friendly, quick and easy
servings: 1
cook time: 5 minutes
date added: 2026-03-25
---

Toast @bread{1%slice} in a #toaster{} until golden.

Spread @butter{1%tbsp} generously over the hot toast. Mix @sugar{1%tsp} and @cinnamon{1/4%tsp} together, then sprinkle evenly over the buttered toast.
